channel.description:

cheers guys I know there is a sticky for compiler questions but whats the point when no one even answers in there.

item.title: Error
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

If your not administrator you oviously dont know the password therefore you cannot compile. Ask the owner of the computer to grant you administartor rights.

If your really desperate press F8 before the Windows boot screen (After BIOS) and boot into Safe Mode. Then press Alt+Ctrl+Del at login screen and type Administrator as your login and leave the password blank.
